          "reviewBody": "Best IB school which is in the heart of the city. Surana hi tech imbibes great values and involves the digital need of the hour for children. Teachers and the staffs are very approachable. Curriculum  is curated well for young minds. My daughter has just joined Pre Kg and is loving to go to school everyday.\nWould highly recommend this school.",
          "publisher": {
