          "datePublished": "2023-10-03",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "We recently shifted to Chennai and were looking for a challenging and contemporary learning environment for our child. Right from our initial meetings to the final orientation, Surana High Tech stood far ahead of the our choices under consideration.\n\nThey’ve effortlessly integrated technology into the traditional Teaching-Learning environment thus creating a highly competitive and conducive setup for self-led inquiry.\n\nThe elements of tradition too have been effortlessly included into the system thereby creating a unique and wonderful educational experience.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
