        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Surana High Tech International School - Besant Nagar"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Srinivasan Vasudevan"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-09-25",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Surana High Tech’s \"Concept-Oriented Learning” instantly resonated with us.Through our own professional journey, we have understood that workplace requires problem solvers with ability to work in an inter-disciplinary environment.\n\nThe school environment integrates technology in innovative & interesting manner to aid learning. Technology is no longer a separate domain , rather will be deeply embedded in all domains as can be seen through recent applications in Finance, Accounting, Legal etc.\n\nSurana High Tech has complemented the digital infrastructure with a great team of Educators and management team who work together to provide this environment.\nOur son loves going to school and has already formed a deep connection with his teacher and his digital buddy :)",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Surana High Tech International School - Besant Nagar"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Vijayshree Mahesh"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-08-30",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The management, principal and staff of Surana High Tech school make a world of difference. My child is currently studying in this school, loves the school and enjoys everyday. They have tailored the IB syllabus to suit indian and chennai culture which is a big plus.\nTruly a wonderful foresight by the team to create such a school in Besant Nagar.\nThe school inside is very much functional as of august 2023 and hoping for the entire school with all amenities to be completed by 2023 end.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
