            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Met the school management regarding admission for my child. Very courteous and professional. Clarified all my doubts regarding IB curriculum. Campus is under construction. It's coming up wonderfully. Very happy with the staff and location of the school too. Everything looks very promising.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
