            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "As a parent of my children, this is my mark of appreciation to SURANA HI TECH INTERNATIONAL SCHOOL that the teachers give an ample drill and practice to the children for developing thinking skills which links the creativity of the children with the concept of the lessons. The students are also assessed with the continuous and comprehensive evaluation which enhances the new features of twenty-first century skills.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
